            woodcutting[2] = 68;
        }
        woodcutting[4] = 1519;
        break;

      case 1307:

      case 2289:

        if (misc.random(2) == 1) {
            woodcutting[2] = 82;
        }
         else {

        }
        woodcutting[4] = 3239;
        break;

      case 9034:
        // Mahogany Tree
        woodcutting[0] = 8;
        woodcutting[1] = 50;
        woodcutting[2] = 125;
        woodcutting[4] = 4445;
        break;

      case 1309:
        // Yew Tree

        woodcutting[1] = 60;
        woodcutting[2] = 175;
        woodcutting[4] = 1515;
        woodcutting[5] = 3;
        break;

      case 1306:
        // Magic Tree
        woodcutting[0] = 10;
        woodcutting[1] = 75;
        woodcutting[2] = 250;
        woodcutting[4] = 1513;
        break;

        /*

        MINING

        // rune essence
        mining[0] = 1;
        mining[1] = 1;
        mining[2] = 5;
        mining[4] = 1436;
        break;
